{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","modules":[{"name":"OpenSwiftUI","relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"]}],"title":"transaction(_:)","externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewPAAE11transactionyQryAA11TransactionVzcF::SYNTHESIZED::s:15OpenSwiftUICore6SpacerV","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method","platforms":[{"name":"iOS","introducedAt":"13.0","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"beta":false},{"name":"macOS","introducedAt":"10.15","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"beta":false},{"name":"tvOS","introducedAt":"13.0","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"beta":false},{"name":"visionOS","introducedAt":"1.0","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"beta":false},{"name":"watchOS","introducedAt":"6.0","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"beta":false}],"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"transaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"((","kind":"text"},{"text":"inout","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Transaction","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"TransactionModifier.swift","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/Animation\/Transaction\/TransactionModifier.swift#L84"}},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/spacer\/transaction(_:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Spacer"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Spacer\/transaction(_:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"text":"Applies the given transaction mutation function to all animations used","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"within the view.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"nonisolated","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"transaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"transform","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"inout","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction","text":"Transaction","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"},{"text":"\n","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The transformation to apply to transactions","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"within this view.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"transform"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A view that wraps this view and applies a transformation to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all transactions used within the view.","type":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this modifier to change or replace the animation used in a view.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Consider three identical animations controlled by a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"button that executes all three animations simultaneously:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The first animation rotates the “Rotation” "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" view by 360"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"degrees."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The second uses the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transaction(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" modifier to change the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"animation by adding a delay to the start of the animation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by two seconds and then increases the rotational speed of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"“Rotation\\nModified” "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text"},{"type":"text","text":" view animation by a factor of 2."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The third animation uses the "},{"code":"transaction(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" modifier to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"replace the rotation animation affecting the “Animation\\nReplaced”"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" view with a spring animation."}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The following code implements these animations:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["struct TransactionExample: View {","    @State private var flag = false","","    var body: some View {","        VStack(spacing: 50) {","            HStack(spacing: 30) {","                Text(\"Rotation\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","","                Text(\"Rotation\\nModified\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction { view in","                        view.animation =","                            view.animation?.delay(2.0).speed(2)","                    }","","                Text(\"Animation\\nReplaced\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction { view in","                        view.animation = .interactiveSpring(","                            response: 0.60,","                            dampingFraction: 0.20,","                            blendDuration: 0.25)","                    }","            }","","            Button(\"Animate\") {","                withAnimation(.easeIn(duration: 2.0)) {","                    self.flag.toggle()","                }","            }","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this modifier on leaf views such as ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Image","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Button","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" rather","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"than container views such as ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/HStack","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":". The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"transformation applies to all child views within this view; calling","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"transaction(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" on a container view can lead to unbounded scope of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"execution depending on the depth of the view hierarchy.","type":"text"}]}]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Image":{"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Image","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"Image","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/image","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Image","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Image","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/VStack":{"title":"VStack","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"VStack"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A view that arranges its subviews in a vertical line."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"VStack"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/vstack"},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Button":{"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Button","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"Button","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/button","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Button","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Button","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Transaction":{"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{